title: Evening on the Bayou (Premium)
description:
This is a preview episode. Get the full episode, and many more, ad free, on our supporter's feed: https://getsleepy.com/support.


Evening on the Bayou
Tonight, we wander languidly along a secluded path to the famous swamplands in southern Louisiana. It's a place full of diverse wildlife, where water and land intermingle as one. 😴 
Sound design: swamp ambiance.
